WEBVTT

00:07:29.667 --> 00:07:30.917
Sometimes it's both.

00:07:32.125 --> 00:07:34.958
With my hometown, that's the way it was.

00:07:36.375 --> 00:07:39.708
For years, our city had changed,

00:07:40.417 --> 00:07:42.625
and it had caused me great pain.

00:07:43.875 --> 00:07:45.351
I remember a childhood

00:07:45.375 --> 00:07:47.792
growing up climbing trees,

00:07:48.708 --> 00:07:51.684
picking mangoes and plums

00:07:51.708 --> 00:07:54.667
on the university campus
where my father was a lecturer.

00:07:55.958 --> 00:08:00.309
Went fishing in the streams
deep in the botanical gardens.